.SH NAME
shelly-open - Open device web UI in browser


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBshelly open  [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Open a Shelly device's web interface in your default browser.

.PP
The device can be specified by:
  - Registered device name
  - IP address
  - Hostname

.PP
This command resolves the device address and opens http://
in your system's default web browser.


